"Black Talon" was the name given to Winchester's Supreme Ammo
 after a very short run there was public outcry as they earned the reputation of being able to shoot through a bullet proof vest, Emergency room Drs .began refusing to treat patients shot with them because the razor sharp pieces of the bullet fragments would cut through their surgical gloves exposing them to blood borne diseases
Bending to political pressure Winchester voluntarily pulled them off the market

(Weapon Armament Surface Protection) is a salt bath ferritic nitrocarburizing surface conversion process or more commonly referred to as nitriding.
